overview: With exclusive access, alongside the candidates and their shadow advisers, this documentary series will take a behind-the-scenes look at the campaign and highlight the backdrop of a merciless struggle for power. How do you make a "presidential"? How to thwart low blows? What alliances to form? How to raise funds, find support? How will everyone prepare for this marathon that can lift them to the highest steps of power or perhaps destroy their political ambitions forever.
